error[E0308]: mismatched types
  --> tests/ui/order_balance_split_cross_side.rs
   |
   |         buy_token_balance: sell_source,
   |                            ^^^^^^^^^^^ expected `BuyTokenDestination`, found `SellTokenSource`
   |
   = note: `SellTokenSource` models the three-variant sell-side allowance path (`Erc20`, `External`, `Internal`); `BuyTokenDestination` models the two-variant buy-side payout path (`Erc20`, `Internal`). The type system rejects any silent cross-side coercion so quote-derived and direct trading-order construction cannot rewrite the buy-side destination.

